## Installation

### Download from the App Store (iPhone and iPad)

1. Open the App Store on your iPhone or iPad.
2. Search for "AI Image to Text Translator" in the search bar.
3. Tap on the app icon in the search results.
4. On the app page, tap the "Get" or "Download" button.
5. Authenticate with your Apple ID, if prompted.
6. Wait for the app to download and install on your device.
7. Once installed, the app icon will appear on your home screen.

## Features

TextSnap offers a range of features to enhance your Language Translation and Learning experience. Explore the following capabilities:

### Offline Translation

TextSnap works with completely AI Trained Language Models. Totally we support 37 Languages in offline. All you need to download the Language models when you start your app or whenever it is required. 
With our Advanced AI powered Image to Text Translator where you can lively click a picture and translate it to your desired language without depending on the internet. 
With our Advanced AI Powered Image to Text Translator where you can chose from gallery and translate it to your desired language without depending on the internet.
Our models are fast and accurate.


### PDF Converter

Now you can convert all the stored or capture Images into PDF Instantly and it supports 37 Languages as well.

### History

You can save all your translation in the history page for future references. 

